### 1C. Assessments Backend

Clinical mental health assessments (PHQ-9, GAD-7, PSS, WHO-5, etc.) with scoring, history, and AI-powered recommendations.

#### Database Schema — `assessments` collection (template definitions)

```json
{
  "_id": ObjectId,
  "name": "PHQ-9 Depression Screening",
  "slug": "phq-9",
  "category": "clinical | wellness",
  "description": "...",
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "text": "Little interest or pleasure in doing things?",
      "options": [
        { "value": 0, "label": "Not at all" },
        { "value": 1, "label": "Several days" },
        { "value": 2, "label": "More than half the days" },
        { "value": 3, "label": "Nearly every day" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "scoring": {
    "ranges": [
      { "min": 0, "max": 4, "label": "Minimal", "severity": "low" },
      { "min": 5, "max": 9, "label": "Mild", "severity": "medium" },
      { "min": 10, "max": 14, "label": "Moderate", "severity": "high" },
      { "min": 15, "max": 27, "label": "Severe", "severity": "critical" }
    ]
  },
  "estimated_minutes": 5,
  "is_active": true
}
```

#### Database Schema — `assessment_results` collection

```json
{
  "_id": ObjectId,
  "user_id": "string",
  "assessment_id": "string (ref: assessments._id)",
  "assessment_slug": "phq-9",
  "answers": [{ "question_id": 1, "value": 2 }],
  "total_score": 14,
  "max_possible_score": 27,
  "percentage": 51.8,
  "severity_label": "Moderate",
  "ai_recommendation": "Based on your moderate depression screening result...",
  "completed_at": "datetime",
  "created_at": "datetime"
}
```

#### [NEW] `backend/app/api/assessments.py`
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/assessments` | List all active assessment templates |
| `GET` | `/assessments/{slug}` | Get a single assessment with questions |
| `POST` | `/assessments/{slug}/submit` | Submit answers, compute score, generate AI recommendation |
| `GET` | `/assessments/history` | Get user's completed assessments |
| `GET` | `/assessments/history/{result_id}` | Get detailed result |

**AI Integration:** After scoring, pass the assessment name + score + severity to the existing `ai_service.generate_empathy_response()` to generate personalized recommendations.

**Seed Data:** Create a management script `backend/scripts/seed_assessments.py` that inserts PHQ-9, GAD-7, PSS-10, WHO-5, and a custom Wellness Check.

**New Packages:** None — uses existing Pydantic + Motor stack.

**Indexes:** `assessment_results`: compound(`user_id` + `completed_at` desc), `assessment_id`

