## Phase 5: Third-Party Integrations
**Priority:** Medium · **Estimated Effort:** ~2-3 days

### 5A. Google Calendar Integration

**Package:** `google-api-python-client`, `google-auth-oauthlib`

```
pip install google-api-python-client google-auth-oauthlib
```

**Flow:**
1. User connects Google account via OAuth2 consent screen (`/auth/google/connect`)
2. Store refresh token in [users](file:///c:/Users/dawoo/Projects/GitHub/TheraAI-FYP-I/backend/app/services/user_service.py#237-261) collection (encrypted field)
3. On appointment creation → create a Google Calendar event with video meeting link
4. On appointment cancellation → delete the calendar event
5. Sync reminder 30 min before session

#### [NEW] `backend/app/services/calendar_service.py`

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `create_event(appointment)` | Creates GCal event with attendees |
| `delete_event(event_id)` | Removes event on cancellation |
| `get_upcoming(user_id)` | Fetches user's upcoming therapy events |

### 5B. Other Recommended Integrations

| Integration | Purpose | Package/API | Priority |
|------------|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Email (Transactional)** | Appointment confirmations, password reset, weekly summaries | `fastapi-mail` + Gmail SMTP (config already exists) | High |
| **Push Notifications** | Appointment reminders, therapist alerts | `firebase-admin` (FCM) | Medium |
| **Payment Gateway** | Real appointment payments | Stripe (`stripe` pip package) or JazzCash/Easypaisa for PKR | Medium |
| **File Storage** | Profile avatars, chat attachments | `boto3` (AWS S3) or local `uploads/` dir | Low |

