## Phase 6: Data Seeding, Polish & Admin Dashboard
**Priority:** Lower · **Estimated Effort:** ~3-4 days

### 6A. Seed Data Strategy

#### [NEW] `backend/scripts/seed.py`

A comprehensive seeding script that populates the database with realistic test data:

```python
# Run: python -m scripts.seed
# Creates:
#   - 5 patient accounts
#   - 3 therapist accounts (with profiles)
#   - 1 admin account
#   - 30 journal entries (spread across patients, various moods)
#   - 20 mood records
#   - 5 assessment templates (PHQ-9, GAD-7, PSS-10, WHO-5, Wellness Check)
#   - 15 assessment results
#   - 10 appointments (mix of statuses)
#   - User settings for each account
```

Use `faker` for realistic names, emails, and text:
```
pip install faker
```

### 6B. Responsiveness Checklist

- [ ] All pages work at `320px` (mobile), `768px` (tablet), `1024px` (desktop), `1440px` (large)
- [ ] SidebarNav collapses to drawer on mobile (already implemented)
- [ ] Cards/grids switch from multi-column to single-column on small screens
- [ ] Modals/dialogs are full-screen on mobile, centered on desktop
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44px on mobile
- [ ] No horizontal scrolling on any viewport

### 6C. Admin Dashboard (Lowest Priority — Deferred)

